Get the whole crew repping your message with team bags and clothes printing.

Team clothing and bags are great ways to showcase team spirit and promote your brand or cause. At VistaPrint, we offer a wide array of customizable options. Some of our best-loved items for teams and groups include classic T-shirts, comfy caps and practical totes. Clothes printing is ideal for work uniforms, team events and more you can even create custom sports team clothing. Plus, with our online design tool, you can design team clothing with personal touches that are unique to each person, like names and numbers.

How to design team bags & clothing

  1. First, browse our clothing and bags collection and choose your favorite. You can use the filters on the left to find the material, size and style that suits your preferences.

  2. Once you've found the right option for you, click on the product to go to the product page. From there, you can pick a material color.

  3. After that, you can upload your own design or create something new in our design studio.

  4. Once you're in the design studio, click on the Team option in the panel on the left.

  5. Decide where to position the placeholders for each person's name and team number (if you want to include them, of course).

  6. Click 'Next' and we'll ask you to provide the details for each member of your team. We'll take care of the rest, printing custom team clothing or bags for each person. And the best part is that you can review all of your personalized items before adding them to your cart.

Personalized team bags and clothing are a great way to ensure that everyone on your team feels included and valued. We even have design experts on hand to help you create a unique, professional-looking design that represents your brand or team in the best possible light. For assistance, just click Need design help? in the bottom right corner of our design studio or visit our help center.

Frequently Asked Questions

Start by selecting your favorite product use the filters on the left to narrow down your options such as decoration type or material. Open the product page from there, you can enter our easy-to-use design studio. You can upload a logo or create a new design from scratch using our custom elements. Click Team in the panel on the left to enter the Team mode and customize with each persons name and team number (optional). When youre done, you can preview each custom item to make sure youre happy with the final look before adding them to your cart.

You can create soccer and basketball uniforms with all-over printing using dye sublimation. This means your design can cover the entire garment without any limitations. Make uniforms that stand out by adding your team's colors to the front, back and sleeves plus, you can even add patterns, text, and images.

The price for clothes or bags printing varies by product, but you can find the price per item on each product page. With VistaPrint, you get great value on custom bags and clothing for groups, as the price per unit goes down the more units you add to your cart.

You have a few options: we offer full-color print, direct-to-garment, embroidery, full-color transfer and dye sublimation. Filter by Decoration in the panel on the left side of the page to find exactly what youre looking for.

Please allow 10+ business days for us to print and ship your items. Find out more about our shipping.

Back printing is possible with some of our clothing. For more details about the decoration area, check the product page.

You need it. We print it. You love it.

VistaPrint is here to help every step of the way.
